@DATABASE "Hyper Active"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - H - Hyper Active"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - H
                   ====================================

                               Hyper Active
                               ============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34548,0)"}          34548,0
@{"Lives = x     " rxs "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34146,255)"}          34146,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).



                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
